Awesome & a Big Thank You! I just wanted to say a very Big Thank you for sharing this recording. I have to say it's one of the best recordings I have ever heard. I just found it.
The best part is that this show was my very first live show, I was 13 yrs old. I remember it well and will never forget it.

Now I know why I kept going back to many, many dead shows throughout the years. To be honest, my first show was the best one and now I get listen to it whenever I want to. Cheers!

PS> I have no idea why there are so few votes or comments for this one, the audio & music is excellent but then I might be biased,
